content: v1xingyue: Merged 4 significant PRs this month, including adding Sui blockchain support (#1693, +10.8k/-1.8k lines), implementing Aggregator swap for Sui tokens (#3012), enhancing price fetching with axios (#2879, +234.8k/-12.7k lines), and adding character URL loading support (#2281, +28k/-2.2k lines). Created one issue (#868) about bringing Move blockchain to Eliza, which has since been closed. Contributed a substantial amount of code with 14 commits modifying 2,491 files (+281k/-20k lines), showing sporadic activity across 6 days this month.
